sentence: Looking at units outstanding versus one week prior within the universe of ETFs covered at ETF Channel, the biggest outflow was seen in the Consumer Discretionary Select Sector SPDR Fund ( XLY ), where 18,000,000 units were destroyed, or a 11.5% decrease week over week.
Among the largest underlying components of XLY, in morning trading today Amazon.com ( AMZN ) is down about 0.4%, and Home Depot ( HD ) is up by about 0.1%.

And on a percentage change basis, the ETF with the biggest outflow was the iShares Currency Hedged MSCI United Kingdom ETF ( HEWU ), which lost 250,000 of its units, representing a 25.0% decline in outstanding units compared to the week prior.
